c: 16
v: 97
t: "Jwalijose jwatatende yambone – chinga jwannume kapena jwankongwe – ni ali jwakulupilila; basi chisimu chene Uwwe chituntamiche jwalakwejo umi wambone (pa dunia pano), soni chisimu (ku Akhera) tuchapa malipilo gao (gamakulungwa nnope) mwakulandanila ni yambone nnope yaŵaliji nkupanganya"